<para id="element-5"><term>Problem : </term> A ball is dropped from a height of 80 m. If the ball looses half its speed after each strike with the horizontal floor, draw (i) speed – time and (ii) velocity – time plots for two strikes with the floor. Consider vertical downward direction as positive and g = 10 
