</m:msup>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-120">
The value of “t” obtained from the equation of ball “A” is : 
</para>
<para id="element-121">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
