</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-122">
Substituting in the equation of ball “B”, we have :
</para>
<para id="element-123"><m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mo> ⇒ </m:mo> 
