<m:mo> ) </m:mo> 
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
<m:mo> } </m:mo> 
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-124">
Now, according to the condition given in the question,
</para>
<para id="element-125">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> A </m:mi>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
